OL,3,CWorkers deaths 'should never have
OL,4,Chappened' says Network Rail
OL,6,FA report into their deaths found an
OL,7,Fofficial lookout was not in place on
OL,8,Fthe day they died.
OL,10,FOn Friday 14 February, Network Rail
OL,11,Fwas fined #3.75 million and ordered to
OL,12,Fpay #175,000 in costs at Swansea Crown
OL,13,FCourt for breaching the Health and
OL,14,FSafety at Work Act 1974.
OL,16,FThe families of Mr Delbridge and Mr
OL,17,FLewis have acknowledged the sentencing
OL,18,Fas an important step in addressing the
OL,19,Fcircumstances that led to their deaths.
