OL,6,FIn a statement, shared by Cari Sowden-
OL,7,FTaylor, Joint Head of the Serious
OL,8,FInjury Team at Hugh James, they said:
OL,9,F"On July 3rd, 2019, Gareth Delbridge
OL,10,Fand Michael Lewis lost their lives in
OL,11,Fan instant, leaving an irreplaceable
OL,12,Fvoid in their families and among those
OL,13,Fwho knew them.
OL,15,F"Their tragic and untimely deaths
OL,16,Fserve as a heartbreaking reminder of
OL,17,Fthe risks faced by railway workers
OL,18,Fevery day.
