OL,3,CWorkers deaths 'should never have
OL,4,Chappened' says Network Rail
OL,6,F"The profound impact of their loss
OL,7,Fcontinues to be felt deeply by their
OL,8,Floved ones, friends, and colleagues.
OL,9,FGareth and Mike were not just workers;
OL,10,Fthey were devoted family members,
OL,11,Fcherished friends, and valued members
OL,12,Fof their community. Their absence is
OL,13,Ffelt in every moment, and the pain of
OL,14,Flosing them remains immeasurable.
OL,16,F"What makes this tragedy even more
OL,17,Fdevastating is that their deaths were
OL,18,Fpreventable. The failure of both their
OL,19,Femployer and the regulator to
OL,20,Fimplement and enforce proper safety
OL,21,Fprotocols cost them their lives.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
