OL,3,CWorkers deaths 'should never have
OL,4,Chappened' says Network Rail
OL,6,F"This should never have happened and
OL,7,Fthere needs to be accountability to
OL,8,Fensure that no other family has to
OL,9,Fendure such unimaginable loss.
OL,11,F"While we acknowledge the progress
OL,12,Fmade in track worker safety since
OL,13,FGareth and Mike's deaths, we urge all
OL,14,Fstakeholders in the railway industry
OL,15,Fto continue prioritising and improving
OL,16,Fsafety measures. No life should be put
OL,17,Fat unnecessary risk due to systemic
OL,18,Ffailures or inadequate protections.
