OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"Though no amount of change can bring
OL,12,FGareth and Mike back, we remain
OL,13,Fsteadfast in our commitment to
OL,14,Fensuring that their deaths lead to
OL,15,Flasting improvements in railway
OL,16,Fsafety. Their legacy must be one of
OL,17,Fchange - change that protects workers,
OL,18,Fsaves lives, and ensures that such a
OL,19,Ftragedy is never repeated."
