OL,3,CWorkers deaths 'should never have
OL,4,Chappened' says Network Rail
OL,6,FNick Millington, Route Director for
OL,7,FNetwork Rail Wales has said "we know
OL,8,Fthat the tragic deaths of our
OL,9,Fcolleagues, Gareth Delbridge and
OL,10,FMichael 'Spike' Lewis, should never
OL,11,Fhave happened on our railway and that
OL,12,Fhas been reflected by today's judgment.
OL,14,F"Over the last five years I have met
OL,15,Fregularly with Gareth and Spike's
OL,16,Ffamilies and our thoughts remain with
OL,17,Fthem."
