OL,6,FHe went on to say, "today's judgment
OL,7,Freinforces why safety must always be
OL,8,Four first consideration, and we will
OL,9,Fcontinue to do all we can to make our
OL,10,Frailways the safest they can be."
OL,12,FThe families remain committed to
OL,13,Fraising awareness of the need for
OL,14,Fstronger safety measures in the
OL,15,Frailway industry to prevent similar
OL,16,Ftragedies.
